Well I found out I might not be able to be a senior next year. I think I might have failed math by like 4 points, so I might have to have summer school, which is totally ok with me, as long as I can take AP Physics and Gov. and Econ next year. So yeah. It's gonna cost me 15 bucks, 100 dollars off. AT JOHNSTON! I hate that school. Why can't it be at Reagan where I know where everything is? I'd even rather go to Lanier. I mean, seriously. But yeah. Jesse has a man lover, Anthony. He has a kid. He is ok. I guess. Now all I gots ta do is find one...And mom said he doesn't even have to be white. YAY. OMG. The only white people worthy of me talking to are like friends...And that is gross. Haha...Well I'm outtie...Someone is IM-ing me. I think it's Lee...Not sure.

 

Peace out.
http://sam-rhs-josh.livejournal.com/31676.html

The last day of school was yesterday. I am sooo happy. I have 3 months and I'll be a senior. I am so glad it's summer. Tomarrow Stela and I might go see "The Longest Yard" with Brandon at Highland 10. I havn't been there since I saw "Team America: World Police"...THAT's a long time...What 4 months, 5 months? Yeah, something like that.

 

Well I have a headache. I'm outtie.

Ok...So Tashia told John that I like him today. I might have a boyfriend by Friday. OMG. I can't wait. But I left school early today and Stela said if I leave early she would tell Servando I like him, so I am hoping she lied to me. I don't want two guys fighting over me. It would cause me too much enjoyment. Haha. I'm kidding. But anyways, I'm getting my hair cut on Saturday. I'd show you how it'll look, but I'm illiterate in that kind of thing...I saved it in my pictures, and I can't find the website I found the picture. So yeah.

 

Well I am outtie. I wanna go smoke a cigarette, and plus me and Jesse are going with mom to Rhonda's house. YAY.

<FONT color=#330033 size=4>I got a freaking 18 on my ACT. I hate myself.</FONT>
http://sam-rhs-josh.livejournal.com/30249.html

I just got back from Fiesta Texas. OMG. I had soooo much fun. Me and Stela went on the Bugs Bunny log ride thing 8 times. I love that ride. I had to dump my shoes dude. They had so much water in them. It isn't even funny.

My feet are all blistered because I wore Nike socks, and they cut off circulation, and my feet were wet. My feet rubbed up against my socks, and my shoes, so DAYUM. I had fun though.

Well, on the ride back I was talking about Servando, the guy I like, and I was messing with a straw in my mouth. I was like, "Yea, Stela. I can talk and move this straw at the same time!!" She was all like, "Servando will be glad to hear that when I tell him on Monday." I freaked. I don't want him to know I like him. That is so embarrassing.

Well, I am outtie. I need to put band-aids on my heels. They hurt. Bye.
http://sam-rhs-josh.livejournal.com/29757.html

AP History test tomarrow. Stela told Servando I like him today, I think. I hate her. Today was Cinco de Mayonnaise. I went to a FIESTA after bass lessons today. Apparently I am really good. I've only been twice, and he says I am gonna be scary once I get good. I was so proud.

Well, I need to finish my English homework. I'm outtie.
http://sam-rhs-josh.livejournal.com/29481.html

Today was the AP test, but I cannot disclose the test info, though. My test will become "invalid". Haha.

I was forced to go to therapy today. I hate that woman. Ohh well.

I burnt my tounge this morning drinking coffee. Owwie. I can't eat spicy things or anything. Damn. So now I am watching CSI. I love this show.

I am going to Fiesta Texas on Saturday. I need to go to Wally World to get my stuff. I am gonna get some "man shorts" and a water-proof camera. Haha. I don't see the point of a fat cow as myself wearing a bathing suit. So yeah.

Carl kicked the fuck outta my shin on Saturday. There is a ton of skin gone, and there is a huge purple bumb. Oww. I think I am gonna need to get my leg amputated. LOL. Anyhoo, I am off to finish my Viet-Nam war project....The American Response and the Draft. WOOO!! Partay.

I saw Robots today. But before that, we went to HEB to get our snacks, and OMG. John was working. I was so happy. Ohhh well. But Robots is the cutest movie ever. I love it. There is a scene where Robin William's character does a full-on Britney Spears impersonation(Hit Me Baby...) to fight off these evil robots. It was awesome. I love that movie. But yeah. I think I am gonna watch Forrest Gump now. "Life is like a box of chocolates. Ya never know what you gunna git." I have loved that movie for years. I think I first saw it when I was like 7 or 8 at my Aunt Billie's house in Cali. We might be going to California in July for a family reunion. YAY. I can't wait to see my Joshy. And Joanne. And maybe Luke. LOL. Anyhoo, I am outtie. Peace up, my neezy's.

He said that black people shouldn't call each other the "n-word" and whites shouldn't call each other crackers, at this point everyone is turned around looking at me, and how mexicans shouldn't call their race whatever they call themselves. The guy was all like, "Let me see the black kids" the whole auditorium raised they hands. He said "Let me see the mexican kids" more raised they hands. You know, I was thinking. It is me, or does it sound odd to have your bf or gf as a "hobby"? That is retarded. Stupid people. 


Man, "Craig" was im-ing me today. Why? I have no clue. He said something about a 91 Firebird or something, and how he bought it from Josh. I don't know. But then he brought up that day after X-Mas when Josh showed up at the mall when me and my brother was there. Why do people keep reminding me of the past? I am trying to forget the past and look on towards the future. 

Me and Jesse went to the mall today. It was ok. Jesse said she had to do my make up, which was fucking hell. I hate make up. I felt all wierd walking thru the mall with that face plaster on. Ewww. But my eyes looked pretty. Purple and red eyeshadow brings out me eyes I guess.

Today I found out that Jason went to Reagan on Frieday to look for me. We came in the cafeteria, during my lunch. He didn't see me though I guess. He told me all these people was mean muggin' him, so he felt wierd and left. So yeah. He skipped school to come see me, which didn't even happen. I need to talk some sense into that boy. LOL. 

But yeah. Prom is on the 21st, and I am gonna wear a tux. I can't stand dresses, and I don't think I would be able to stand being in one for 6 or 7 hours. So, I am wearing a tux. I am getting my hair cut off, it's "pixie". I think that is what they call it. Dunno. it is orange-red. I am getting my make up did as well. Mom said if I am going in a tux, my face better look decent. I can't wait to get shit-faced and party it up at either Owens on I-35 or Denny''s on I-35 off of St. Johns. Yeah bitches.


Well, I have to figure out who I am going to prom with. I think I am gonna ask out Jason tomarrow. Yay. I can't wait.

Yabbbity dooodah.

Love Always,
